data.description: What a nice house.   Large covered entry with columns and double door opens to open floor plan with cathedral ceiling.   Large great room, Kitchen with new cabinets, open bar seating, and dining area looks out to back screen room and yard.  Split bedroom plan.   One room ideal for office or play room with a concealed murphy wall bed.  Master bath has his and her vanities and soaking tub and shower, large walk in closet.   Two car garage. Fenced area in back yard for pet.  This is a larger home in a convenient location to shopping and schools. HVAC is only two years old.  Don't miss this house.
